					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6290006#post-3860194</guid>
				<title>Are Bound To Repeat It.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6290006/scp-4160#post-3860194</link>
